ed="T" n="0757c18"/><persName key="A010106">釋道亮</persName>，姓朱氏，<placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName>人也。厥考前刺<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽<lb
ed="T" n="0757c19"/>郡</placeName><ptr target="#n1344"/>。<persName key="A010106">亮</persName>年<ref target="#j19518931952258" type="date">八歲</ref>出家，極通經業。受具後學「河<lb
ed="T" n="0757c20"/>中三論」<ptr type="glossary" target="#g813"/>，復講《涅槃經》。尋入深谷，破衣覆形，<lb
ed="T" n="0757c21"/>蔬食資命，不交俗務，直守童真<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1382"/>。<date from-iso="+0705-02-25" key="j19786111978942" to-iso="+0706-01-22"><name>神龍</name>元年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0757c22"/><persName key="A002100">孝和皇帝</persName>詔<persName key="A010106">亮</persName>與法席宗師十人，入<placeName key="PL000000042362">長樂大<lb
ed="T" n="0757c23"/>內</placeName>坐夏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g61"/>安居。時<ref type="person" target="#A002100">帝</ref>命受菩薩戒。<persName key="A002461">睿宗</persName>及妃后<lb
ed="T" n="0757c24"/>送異錦衾氈席。<date from-iso="+0706-01-23" key="j19789431979326" to-iso="+0707-02-10">二年</date>，詔於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042284">西園</ref>問道，朝廷<lb
ed="T" n="0757c25"/>欽貴。大都督<persName key="A010118">李孝逸</persName>、工部尚書<persName key="A010116">張錫</persName>、國子監<lb
ed="T" n="0757c26"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>周</sic><corr>司</corr></choice>業<persName key="A010112">崔融</persName><ptr target="#n1160"/>、祕書監<persName key="A008710">賀知章</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000012005">睦州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A010832">康<add resp="sgsz">希</add>詵</persName><ptr target="#n1345"/>，同<lb
ed="T" n="0757c27"/>心慕仰，請問禪心，多結師資，或傳香火<ptr target="#n1346"/>。卒<lb
ed="T" n="0757c28"/>年八十二，門人<persName key="A010110">慧遠</persName>等建塔，<persName key="A007959">萬齊融</persName>為銘紀<lb
ed="T" n="0757c29"/>述。</p>
